{"tid":24403,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"2004年中上左車，你問我答","createTime":"2016-12-05T13:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T09:22:22.000Z","uid":6324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52dc40bbf9ebec24037c296b6f532237c425aaa8","tid":24403,"uid":6324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:33:47.000Z","msg":"大家一齊交流下"},{"pid":"3aa15b97b99277ebaf83c506cea55d9180d6ebe2","tid":24403,"uid":24527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:38:44.000Z","msg":"幾錢買？首期幾多？<br />\n果陣月入幾多？供幾多？<br />\n有冇老婆同你一齊供？<br />\n而家月入幾多？<br />\n升值幾多？<br />\n仲有幾多年未供？"},{"pid":"6650e3c4244eabea52db07d56897210198c1194c","tid":24403,"uid":44980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:53:05.000Z","msg":"她年僅27歲便上車，2年內已「供斷層樓」，04年時以300萬在將軍澳購入一個900呎的單位，現時更有樓有舖，擁有過千萬資產。她說買樓之道最重要是信念和付出，自言生活沒什麼娛樂；找工作亦不講夢想只向錢看；不會想儲多少錢，反而要規定自己只花多少錢。她又指時下年青人缺乏機會去體驗別人的艱苦，「唔知自己有幾幸福」，故缺少動力上游<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8fc42daa5ac460e4af0b2f14118147298c684d","tid":24403,"uid":6324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:30:33.000Z","msg":"358萬買"},{"pid":"a353b0ae7ff6f28eeab5da7f1dd056f8bf469bec","tid":24403,"uid":6324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:31:31.000Z","msg":"果陣月入三萬唔夠"},{"pid":"d465a2a478073f7d0d0e7589982825fdf2f79718","tid":24403,"uid":6324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:31:59.000Z","msg":"有老婆一齊供"},{"pid":"e4abe0707bb461d1361cfe8f1729cc53575f56b7","tid":24403,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:14:41.000Z","msg":"其實我諗無人有興趣知靠樓升發達既故事"},{"pid":"679ae0d0d9d9b0799415441dea8ef47fbc643403","tid":24403,"uid":44980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:26:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我諗無人有興趣知靠樓升發達既故事</blockquote><br />\n但樓主好想講佢